48
00:03:43,791 --> 00:03:44,958
Hati-hati.

49
00:04:36,958 --> 00:04:38,458
Darko, kita akan keluar.

50
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:40,875
Perhatikan lereng.

51
00:04:42,833 --> 00:04:44,083
Kami periksa trak.

52
