56
00:05:46,958 --> 00:05:48,708
Celaka!

57
00:06:02,291 --> 00:06:03,125
Tidak!

58
00:06:12,958 --> 00:06:14,291
Trak-trak itu kosong.

59
00:06:15,083 --> 00:06:18,083
<i>Mereka punggah 90 tan emas</i>
<i>dalam setengah jam, ini…</i>

60
00:06:18,166 --> 00:06:20,500
Maksudnya, mereka tahu rancangan kita.

61
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:22,833
Seorang saja yang mampu curi emas itu.

62
00:06:27,083 --> 00:06:29,083
Awak kenal dia.

63
00:06:29,166 --> 00:06:31,250
Tak! Dia tahu tentang sasaran kita.

64
