69
00:06:44,916 --> 00:06:47,041
Ya! Sebab ia nyawa kita semua!

70
00:06:47,125 --> 00:06:49,041
Orang bercakap di ranjang.

71
00:06:49,125 --> 00:06:50,541
<i>Awak pun tak terkecuali.</i>

72
00:06:51,750 --> 00:06:56,375
Awak beritahu saya rancangan Paris
