00:07:41,250 --> 00:07:43,041
Bekas isteri abang saya.

85
00:07:43,625 --> 00:07:45,500
Bagus. Apa pekerjaan dia?

86
00:07:46,833 --> 00:07:47,916
Dia pemain piano

87
00:07:49,416 --> 00:07:51,000
dan pencuri!

88
00:07:59,041 --> 00:08:03,791
Dia tahu segala-galanya!

89
00:08:29,583 --> 00:08:32,832
Selama ini,
