90
00:08:33,332 --> 00:08:34,582
Mereka tahu semuanya.

91
00:08:35,582 --> 00:08:37,416
Mereka cuma tunggu masa.

92
00:08:38,707 --> 00:08:41,250
Mereka tahu selepas trak-trak itu masuk,

93
00:08:41,332 --> 00:08:45,666
kita cuma ada lapan
hingga sepuluh jam dan sebab itulah,

94
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,083
mereka datang tepat pada masanya.

95
00:09:01,625 --> 00:09:03,333
Cepat sedikit!

96
00:09:03,416 --> 00:09:04,375
Ayuh, semua!

97
00:09:04,458 --> 00:09:06,666
Ayuh! Cepat!

98
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:07,750
<i>Lekas!</i>

99
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:12,500
<i>Beri laluan!</i>

100
00:09:12,583 --> 00:09:14,875
Ayuh! Okey, bagus.

101
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:17,041
