102
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:21,125
- Lapan minit saja lagi!
- Lekas!

103
00:09:21,208 --> 00:09:22,333
Ayuh!

104
00:09:22,875 --> 00:09:23,958
Mari pergi!

105
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,000
<i>Mesej ini untuk semua orang.</i>

106
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:19,958
<i>Emas kita dah dicuri.</i>

107
00:10:22,250 --> 00:10:25,625
<i>Mereka menyamar jadi polis</i>
<i>dan serbu tangki air ribut.</i>

108
00:10:26,625 --> 00:10:28,000
<i>Kita akan kejar mereka.</i>

109
00:10:28,916 --> 00:10:31,375
Mereka guna lori jongket.

110
00:10:31,458 --> 00:10:34,708
Mereka isinya dengan jongkong
dan kambus dengan pasir.

111
00:10:35,458 --> 00:10:38,125
<i>Ia terdedah</i>
<i>supaya tak nampak mencurigakan.</i>

112
00:10:38,208 --> 00:10:40,916
Tiada sesiapa boleh tahu
