113
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,291
<i>Tebusan, polis atau sesiapa saja.</i>

114
00:10:43,375 --> 00:10:46,666
<i>Matilah kita</i>
<i>kalau ada apa-apa masalah lagi, faham?</i>

115
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:47,625
Saya faham.

116
