129
00:11:23,541 --> 00:11:26,916
<i>fikir satu subjek</i>
<i>yang kamu nak belajar di penjara nanti.</i>

130
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,166
<i>Saya janji.</i>

131
00:11:30,208 --> 00:11:31,625
Kita akan jumpa emas itu

