167
00:15:33,041 --> 00:15:34,541
<i>Pada hari geng itu kalah,</i>

168
00:15:35,458 --> 00:15:38,166
<i>kami semua teringat</i>
<i>tentang kejadian ikan itu.</i>

169
00:15:39,333 --> 00:15:43,000
<i>Namun, kami tak leka</i>
<i>walaupun perlu lepaskan tekanan.</i>

170
00:15:43,833 --> 00:15:46,208
<i>Kami kecewa emas itu hilang</i>.

171
00:15:46,291 --> 00:15:50,166
<i>Hakikatnya, keyakinan kami</i>
